{"word":"G5303 - ὑστέρημα - hystérēma - hoos-ter'-ay-mah - That which is behind","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑστέρημα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hystérēma</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoos-ter'-ay-mah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">That which is behind</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"வறுமை குறைவு - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. deficiency, that which is lacking"},{"paragraph":"2. poverty, want, destitution"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5302 - ὑστερέω - hysteréō - hoos-ter-eh'-o/5302\">G5302</a>; a <i>deficit</i>; specifically <i>poverty:</i> - that which is behind, (that which was) lack (-ing), penury, want.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5302/5302\">G5302</a>, <a href=\"#/G5303/5303\">G5303</a>, <a href=\"#/G5304/5304\">G5304</a>, <a href=\"#/G5305/5305\">G5305</a>, <a href=\"#/G5306/5306\">G5306</a>, <a href=\"#/G650/650\">G650</a>"}]}